Title: Unliving Summons
Description:
We need you in Tirisfal, $n. Come quickly.

There's a new situation brewing just outside the Ruins of Lordaeron, and it's not looking pretty. I'll get you up to speed when you arrive.
ObjectivesText: Report to Lilian Voss in the Ruins of Lordaeron.
PortraitTurnInText: Speak to her in the Ruins of Lordaeron in Tirisfal Glades.
